{"Id":103,"LanguageCodes":["en","eng"],"Name":"eng-aishabewley","Author":"Aisha Bewley","Language":"English","Description":"English","Direction":"ltr","Source":"","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"When the Great Event occurs"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"none will deny its occurrence"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"bringing low, raising high"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"When the earth is convulsed"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"and the mountains are crushed"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"and become scattered dust in the air"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"And you will be classed into three"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"the Companions of the Right: what of the Companions of the Right"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"the Companions of the Left: what of the Companions of the Left"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"and the Forerunners, the Forerunners"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"Those are the Ones Brought Near"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"in Gardens of Delight"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"A large group of the earlier people"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"but few of the later ones"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"On sumptuous woven couches"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"reclining on them face to face"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"There will circulate among them, ageless youths"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"carrying goblets and decanters and a cup from a flowing spring —"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"it does not give them any headache nor does it leave them stupefied"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"And any fruit they specify"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"and any bird-meat they desire"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"And dark-eyed maidens"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"like hidden pearls"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"As recompense for what they did"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"They will hear no prattling in it nor any word of wrong"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"All that is said is, ´Peace! Peace!´"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"And the Companions of the Right: what of the Companions of the Right"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"Amid thornless lote-trees"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"and fruit-laden acacias"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"and wide-spreading shade"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"and outpouring water"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"and fruits in abundance"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"never failing, unrestricted"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"And on elevated couches"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"We have brought maidens into being"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"and made them purest virgins"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"devoted, passionate, of like age"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"for the Companions of the Right"}]}